cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper deals with learning a latent representation space for sequential processes, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of computer vision techniques, which suggests that cs.CV (Computer Vision) may also be a relevant sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with control and decision-making in sequential processes, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
